  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in Hyperhidrosis Disease Severity Scale.</measure>
    <time_frame>baseline to 12 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>Hyperhidrosis Disease Severity Scale measurement is based of 1-4 points. Score 1 is the lowest severity and score 4 would be the highest severity for sweating.</description>
